OL,3,CFirst designs of Jersey's new #710m
OL,4,CHospital unveiled to the public
OL,6,FThe first designs of 's new Acute
OL,7,FHospital at Overdale have been
OL,8,Funveiled to the public.
OL,10,FThe building is set to cost upwards of
OL,11,F#700m - with plans for all of the
OL,12,Fisland's health facilities eventually
OL,13,Ftopping #1bn.
OL,15,FA planning application is due to be
OL,16,Fsubmitted by the end of 2024, with
OL,17,Fbuilding work expected to start in
OL,18,F2025 - it is hoped the facility will
OL,19,Fbe open by 2028.
