OL,3,CFirst designs of Jersey's new #710m
OL,4,CHospital unveiled to the public
OL,6,FThe dilapidated and unused healthcare
OL,7,Fbuildings at the back of the Overdale
OL,8,Fsite are already being demolished and
OL,9,Fare set to be cleared by the end of
OL,10,Fthe year.
OL,12,FThe facility will increase bed
OL,13,Fcapacity in the island by 80 and
OL,14,Finclude the following: an A&E
OL,15,Fdepartment, a critical care unit, a
OL,16,Fwomen's and children's centre
OL,17,F(including maternity unit), elective
OL,18,Fand emergency operating theatres, and
OL,19,Finpatient wards.
