OL,3,CFirst designs of Jersey's new #710m
OL,4,CHospital unveiled to the public
OL,6,FMost inpatient beds will be single
OL,7,Frooms with en-suite bathrooms.
OL,9,FDeputy Tom Binet, Jersey's Minister
OL,10,Ffor Health and Social Services, said:
OL,11,F"We are making very good progress with
OL,12,Fthe development of the Acute Hospital,
OL,13,Fwhich I hope islanders will see
OL,14,Freflected in the concept designs we
OL,15,Fare sharing at this stage.
OL,17,F"I look forward to presenting the
OL,18,Fscheme to islanders in much more
OL,19,Fdetail in the coming months when we
OL,20,Fwill be going out to public
OL,21,Fconsultation."
