OL,3,CFirst designs of Jersey's new #710m
OL,4,CHospital unveiled to the public
OL,6,FMeetings will now take place to gather
OL,7,Ffeedback on the designs which, the
OL,8,Fgovernment says, will inform the next
OL,9,Fstage of the building's design.
OL,11,FResidents of Overdale and Kensington
OL,12,FPlace will also be invited to the next
OL,13,F'Neighbourhood Forum' to hear more
OL,14,Fabout the project.
OL,16,FAn island-wide consultation will then
OL,17,Ftake place in May 2024 when residents
OL,18,Fwill be able to give feedback on the
OL,19,Fproposals.
