OL,4,CHospital unveiled to the public
OL,6,FDeputy Binet added: "I hope that by
OL,7,Fsharing the designs at this stage
OL,8,Fmeans that our community can get a
OL,9,Fgood sense of the fantastic new
OL,10,Ffacility that is being developed.
OL,12,F"Engaging with key stakeholders at
OL,13,Fthis stage of the process is essential
OL,14,Fto make sure we are capturing feedback
OL,15,Ffrom those who are more likely to be
OL,16,Fimpacted by the proposals."
